// LANG.md §9.1 (ADR-042): a standalone component — a `component` with no `for`
// parent — is a context-layer node beside persons and systems, exactly as a
// standalone container is. Its cross-boundary call to `Backend` renders as a
// context-layer edge.

//! m

public system Backend {
  Serve(): void;
}

public component Widget {
  Handle(): void { m::Backend.Serve() }
}
